              "content": "Exports the requested resources and returns them as a downloadable ZIP archive. Each exported resource is placed in a separate file (optionally inside a sub-folder determined by `folderPath`). When template variables are detected across the exported resources, a `.env` file is automatically generated and included in the ZIP root; the `.env` file is omitted when no template variables are found.\n",
              "type": "text/plain"
            },
